### Get all products
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products

###

### Get products sorted by price (descending)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products?sortBy=price&sortOrder=desc

###

### Get products sorted by name (ascending)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products?sortBy=name&sortOrder=asc

###

### Filter by category
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products?category=Electronics

###

### Filter by price range
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products?minPrice=50&maxPrice=500

###

### Search by name
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products?search=Laptop

###

### Combined filters and sorting
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products?category=Electronics&sortBy=price&sortOrder=asc&minPrice=20&maxPrice=200

###

### Get product by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products/1

###

### Get all categories
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products/categories

###

### Create a new product
POST http://localhost:5000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Gaming Mouse",
  "category": "Electronics",
  "price": 59.99,
  "stock": 30
}

###

### Update a product
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Laptop",
  "category": "Electronics",
  "price": 1299.99,
  "stock": 12
}

###

### Delete a product
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/products/1

###
